10 REM THIS IS A SIMPLE TENNIS GAME.
20 REM THE PLAYERS ARE 32x16 SPRITES.
30 REM THE BALL IS A 32x32 SPRITE.

200 PRINT CHR$(147)
210 PRINT "INITIALIZING. PLEASE WAIT..."

1000 REM INITIALIZE PLAYER SPRITE DATA
1010 ADDR=$8000
1020 FOR I=0TO15
1030 FOR J=0TO3
1040 READ A
1050 FOR K=0TO7
1060 BI=INT(A/128)
1070 B=BI*$FF
1080 VPOKE $0, ADDR, BI
1090 ADDR=ADDR+1
1100 A=(A-128*BI)*2
1110 NEXT K
1120 NEXT J
1130 NEXT I

1200 REM INITIALIZE BALL SPRITE DATA
